vote.title: An ordinance amending Chapter 50, “Consumer Affairs,” of the Dallas City Code by amending Article XI (1) providing regulations for credit services organizations and additional requirements for credit access businesses; (2) providing a penalty not to exceed $500.00; (3) providing a saving clause; (4) providing a severability clause; and (5) providing an effective date - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
